		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Those who swear an oath of vengeance choose to hunt down creatures who have wronged others. Sometimes an avenger hunts a specific organization or group of creatures, and sometimes an avenger simply tries to destroy evil. Some avengers become obsessive or selfishly focused on a campaign of vengeance, but usually paladins following this path put protecting others above all else. Avengers are powerful at punishing and locking down foes.</p><p></p><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>Avenger</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Features</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.wjflquP9J7ItZqny]{Avenger's Leap} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MUXZKqXOk5k1w8pS]{Commanding Challenge}</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.2yjAwCh8FpQP0MAP]{Searing Retribution}</td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.wjflquP9J7ItZqny]{Avenger's Leap} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MUXZKqXOk5k1w8pS]{Commanding Challenge}</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.xrqF7vKMSesGLGPq]{Avenger's Vow}</td></tr><tr><td>20</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.fliH2ub4KtFOh0KU]{Avatar of Vengeance}</td></tr></tbody></table><table data-toc-level=\"3\"><caption>Expanded Spell List</caption><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Paladin Level</th><th scope=\"col\">Extra Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.YthqhHtddDfGMNHB]{Bane}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.SZi4TOafYgqm0A0n]{Shadow Strike}</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.2S4Lb8HB2ukb7uBT]{Hold Creature}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Wp9ckwdiUpIuPE5l]{See Invisibil